      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prom-tip"
      },
      "description": "Pending txs not yet committed, per node.\n\nNormal: ~0 (keeping up).\nAct if: climbing steadily, offered load exceeds throughput; this is the capacity knee. CPU-profile a node here to see the wall (state-root / commit-handler / crypto).",
